title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 33500
description:
Well as I post this the entire North Eastern Seaboard of America are under record snowfalls.  As a Scotsman who lived for 6 years in Central Canada in a town called Timmins, in addition to spending 6 months in the British Antarctic on board the RRS Earnest Shackleton, I know only too well what that is like.

Stay warm and safe, and have some fun with this batch of 300 Karaoke songs in CDG+MP3
Format.

Rigmar Radio - Seeding to the World since 2004

Oh and PS Thanks for seeding :-)
